OL,3,CCare-leavers endured 'lengthy and
OL,4,Coften traumatic' wait for personal data
OL,6,FReport by ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,8,FProducer Lottie Kilraine
OL,10,FMany adults who spent time in
OL,11,Fresidential care as children have
OL,12,Fendured a "lengthy, demoralising and
OL,13,Foften traumatic process" - sometimes
OL,14,Fwaiting up to 16 years to receive
OL,15,Ftheir personal records, which often
OL,16,Farrive heavily redacted or damaged,
OL,17,Fnew research has found.
