OL,3,CCare-leavers endured 'lengthy and
OL,4,Coften traumatic' wait for personal data
OL,6,FIn an urgent letter sent to local
OL,7,Fauthority leaders today, the
OL,8,FInformation Commissioner (ICO) has
OL,9,Fsaid that if improvements are not
OL,10,Fmade, organisations may face
OL,11,Fregulatory action.
OL,13,FJohn-george Nicholson, 48, from
OL,14,FLondon, grew up in care and was only
OL,15,Fable to access heavily redacted files
OL,16,Fwhen he first applied for his personal
OL,17,Frecords in his 20s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
