OL,3,CCare-leavers endured 'lengthy and
OL,4,Coften traumatic' wait for personal data
OL,6,FCare-leavers can submit a subject
OL,7,Faccess request (SAR) to organisations,
OL,8,Fwhich can provide information such as
OL,9,Fphotographs and social worker reports,
OL,10,Fwhich the ICO says often helps them
OL,11,Fpiece together "their own story".
OL,13,FBut lengthy delays, with some people
OL,14,Fwaiting decades, and heavily redacted
OL,15,Frecords, as well as challenges
OL,16,Faccessing support, are among the
OL,17,Fproblems many have come up against,
OL,18,Faccording to the commissioner's office.
