OL,6,FThe ICO recently served Bristol City
OL,7,FCouncil with an enforcement notice for
OL,8,Fundue delays involving child social
OL,9,Fcare data, and fined Scottish charity
OL,10,FBirthlink #18,000 after it destroyed
OL,11,Fthousands of records, including
OL,12,Fhandwritten letters and photographs.
OL,14,FMr Nicholson described receiving his
OL,15,Frecords as "tough and often traumatic
OL,16,Fto read" but said people who have
OL,17,Fspent time in the care system deserve
OL,18,Faccess to their personal information
OL,19,Fto help them "make sense" of their
OL,20,Fpast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
