OL,4,Coften traumatic' wait for personal data
OL,6,F"I was just a kid in a broken system,"
OL,7,Fhe said. "But the system is still
OL,8,Fbroken, and record-keeping is a
OL,9,Fcritical element of this - our
OL,10,Fstorytelling.
OL,12,F"Too often the whole child is lost in
OL,13,Fforms and reports, their voice
OL,14,Fminimised or unheard. That has to
OL,15,Fchange."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
