OL,6,FJackie McCartney, who grew up in the
OL,7,Fcare system and is now an ambassador
OL,8,Ffor care charity the Rees Foundation,
OL,9,Fdescribed a similar experience and
OL,10,Fsaid her records had arrived in "one
OL,11,Fold battered brown box".
OL,13,F"That was all I was worth," she said.
OL,14,F"That box was my life story of
OL,15,Fresidential care, with 16 years of my
OL,16,Flife inside.
