OL,6,F"I opened my box and looked inside. I
OL,7,Fcan still feel the pain and
OL,8,Fdisappointment. My records were not
OL,9,Feven in date order, with whole years
OL,10,Fof my life missing and no medical
OL,11,Frecords. There were so many blank
OL,12,Fpages with nothing on, and so much
OL,13,Finformation redacted."
