OL,3,CCare-leavers endured 'lengthy and
OL,4,Coften traumatic' wait for personal data
OL,6,FThe ICO is calling for urgent
OL,7,Fimprovements in how care records are
OL,8,Fbuilt and accessed from local
OL,9,Fauthorities across the country,
OL,10,Fincluding new standards for
OL,11,Forganisations providing clarity on how
OL,12,Fto handle requests with care and a UK-
OL,13,Fwide supervision pilot running across
OL,14,F2025/26, monitoring the performance of
OL,15,F19 organisations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
