OL,6,FHe added that councils should have
OL,7,Fsufficient resources to enable them to
OL,8,Fmanage the volume and complexity of
OL,9,Frequests "without delay and further
OL,10,Fharm".
OL,12,FThroughout our forced adoption
OL,13,Finvestigation, ITV News has been
OL,14,Fcontacted by dozens of people who were
OL,15,Fadopted as children, who tell us of
OL,16,Fthe struggle they are still facing to
OL,17,Fget any transparency over information
OL,18,Fthey feel they have a right to have.
