OL,6,FThis includes some being told their
OL,7,Ffiles have "been destroyed" or lost,
OL,8,For given pages of unexplained
OL,9,Fredactions by councils, religious
OL,10,Fgroups and charities.
OL,12,FLast week, the Adult Adoptee Movement
OL,13,Fmet the Secretary of State for
OL,14,FEducation, whose department handles
OL,15,Fadoption, for the first time to urge
OL,16,Fher to listen to those with lived
OL,17,Fexperience and push for improved
OL,18,Faccess to records.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
